snippet.textDisplay:
Ki Muhammad ((SAWW)) saay wafa tou ney tu hum teray hain, Ye jahan cheez hai kya loh-o-Qalam teray hain ~ Allama Iqbal, the great.
     I am at the university campus but couldn't stop myself from clicking on it, looking at this notification. 'Shikwa and Jawab-e-Shikwa' is literally life for any Muslim and especially in this era of darkness and chaos. So so so excited for this one, i hope the utter depth and sharp spiritual touch would be well presented and maintained through singing/reciting. All the best CSP -11 !!!
